OL,7,F"The Labour Party made promises to us,
OL,8,Falongside dozens of other victims of
OL,9,Fpress intrusion" said Gerry McCann.
OL,11,F"Only Leveson part two will provide
OL,12,Fjustice to those of us who have
OL,13,Fsuffered at the hands of the press."
OL,15,F"It is critical that this government
OL,16,Fhas the courage and integrity to keep
OL,17,Fthose promises and proceed with the
OL,18,Fsecond half of the Leveson Inquiry."
