OL,7,FIn 2011, Gerry and Kate McCann gave
OL,8,Fevidence to the Leveson Inquiry, a
OL,9,Fpublic inquiry launched in the wake of
OL,10,Fthe News of the World phone hacking
OL,11,Fscandal.
OL,13,FKate McCann told the Inquiry she felt
OL,14,F"totally violated" by the way she'd
OL,15,Fbeen treated by the tabloids,
OL,16,Ffollowing the disappearance of her
OL,17,Fdaughter, saying "there was absolutely
OL,18,Fno respect shown for me as a grieving
OL,19,Fmother".
