OL,7,FThere was meant to be a second part of
OL,8,Fthe Inquiry looking into unlawful
OL,9,Fconduct within media organisations and
OL,10,Fthe relationship between journalists
OL,11,Fand the police, but it was cancelled
OL,12,Fby the Conservative government in 2018.
OL,14,FUnder Jeremy Corbyn, Labour was
OL,15,Fcommitted to holding Leveson Part Two.
OL,17,FThe prime minister told ITV News that
OL,18,Fthe second half of the Leveson inquiry
OL,19,Fis not among the Labour government's
OL,20,Fpriorities
