OL,7,FBut when ITV News put Gerry McCann's
OL,8,Fstatement to the Prime Minister, Keir
OL,9,FStarmer, today he ruled it out.
OL,11,F"We set out in our manifesto our
OL,12,Fprogramme for action for this
OL,13,Fgovernment, we've laid that out in the
OL,14,FKing's Speech, that clearly sets out
OL,15,Four priorities - and the second half
OL,16,Fof Leveson is not among them," he said.
