OL,7,FPrince Harry told ITV News that the
OL,8,Fdecision to fight public court battles
OL,9,Fagainst the tabloid press is a "centre
OL,10,Fpiece" to why he has fallen out with
OL,11,Fhis family.
OL,13,FHe said: "I have made it very clear
OL,14,Fthat this is something that needs to
OL,15,Fbe done, it would be nice if we did it
OL,16,Fas a family.
OL,18,F"It has caused part of a rift."
