OL,7,F"To have the judge rule in our favour
OL,8,Fwas obviously huge. But for him to go
OL,9,Fas far as he did... this wasn't just
OL,10,Fthe individual people. This went right
OL,11,Fup to the top. This was lawyers, this
OL,12,Fwas high executives. And to be able to
OL,13,Fachieve that in a trial that's a
OL,14,Fmonumental victory."
OL,16,FThe decision to fight public court
OL,17,Fbattles against the tabloid press is a
OL,18,F'central piece' to why Prince Harry
OL,19,Fhas fallen out with his family, he says
