OL,7,FIn December 2023, a judge ruled that
OL,8,FPrince Harry's voicemails had been
OL,9,Fintercepted and his private
OL,10,Finformation unlawfully obtained by the
OL,11,FDaily Mirror, Sunday Mirror and The
OL,12,FPeople.
OL,14,FPrince Harry said it had caused him
OL,15,F"paranoia, fear and distrust" and that
OL,16,Fhis mother Princess Diana "motivates"
OL,17,Fhim in his legal battles against the
OL,18,Ftabloids.
